Source code and simulation data for the paper 'Multi-Ciliated Microswimmers â€“ Metachronal
Coordination and Helical Swimming' by Sebastian Rode, Jens Elgeti, and Gerhard
Gompper

src/ - C++ source files for the MPC simulation
create.py - Python script to generate raw data
process.py - Python script for data pre-processing
requirements.txt  - Python dependencies


The paper figures can be reproduced with the attached jupyter notebooks.

Full simulation can be run via the cilia executable and the corresponding config file:
./src/cilia sim.cfg
